<br>
I just think you should have to activate autorun if you want it, only takes a second to hit num lock. I know it can be argued from the other side, that it only takes a sec to disable it, but the normal state of your character should be at rest, and only be moved when you make a specific command, character should not move on its own. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=639407" target="top">Kozul Goodheart</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
