<br>
Pressing UP in chat bar caused you to move forward, just like when you're not in the chat bar.<br>
<br>
Became Broken:<br>
<br>
Pressing UP in chat bar did nothing.<br>
<br>
After Patch:<br>
<br>
Pressing UP in chat bar turns on Auto Run, and you die.<br>
<br>
This is the issue, I think, for those who aren't getting it.<br>
